# Ejemplo de Template con coloreado

Document (@stxt.template):
	Structure >>
		Title: Simple text
		Author (dc): Person name
		Section >>
			Heading: Section title
			Paragraph: Content text
			Code (@example): Source code
	
	Description >>
		Document (@stxt.template): Template definition
			Title: The document title
			Author (dc): Author of the document
			Section: Main content section
				Heading: Section heading text
				Paragraph: Section paragraph content
				Code (@example): Example code block

# Otro ejemplo de template

Person (@stxt.template):
	Structure >>
		Name: Full name
		Age: Integer value
		Email (contact): Email address
		Phone (contact): Phone number
	
	Description >>
		Person (@stxt.template): Person information
			Name: Person's full name
			Age: Person's age in years
			Email (contact): Contact email address
			Phone (contact): Contact phone number
